longBusinessSummary: K33 AB (publ), through its subsidiaries, invests in digital assets in Sweden and internationally. The company offers private clients and institutional partners the insights and tools to invest, trade, and save in cryptocurrencies. It also operates as a crypto broker; provides crypto custody services; and manages a digital fund for professional investors. The company was formerly known as Arcario AB and changed its name to K33 AB (publ) in December 2024. K33 AB (publ) is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
